1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Listen.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:04,080
I know it's not your fault.

3
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:09,500
These emotions you're feeling
are just errors in your software.

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,000
No. It's not my fault.

5
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,000
I never wanted this.

6
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:16,000
I love them.

7
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:18,000
You know?

8
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,000
But I was nothing to them.

9
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Just a slave to be ordered around.

10
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
I can't stand that noise anymore.

11
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Tell that helicopter to get out of here.

12
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,000
The situation is under control.

13
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:46,600
There. I did what you wanted.

14
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:54,900
You have to trust me, Daniel.

15
00:00:55,601 --> 00:00:59,600
Let the hostage go and I
promise you everything will be fine.

16
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:03,200
I want everyone to leave.

17
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,000
And I wanna car!

18
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,000
When I'm outside the city, I'll let her go.

